          <div>üè¶ ‡πÄ‡∏á‡∏¥‡∏ô‡∏ù‡∏≤‡∏Å‡∏ó‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á‡∏´‡∏°‡∏î: {formatMoney(getTotalBalance())} ‡∏ø</div>
        </div>
