          {accountInfo.monthlyFee && (
            <div className="stat-row fee-info">
              <span>‡∏Ñ‡πà‡∏≤‡∏ö‡∏≥‡∏£‡∏∏‡∏á‡∏£‡∏≤‡∏¢‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏ô:</span>
