          {accountInfo.interestRate > 0 ? (
            <div className="calculator">
              <p>
                ‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏ù‡∏≤‡∏Å <strong>1,000 ‡∏ø</strong> ‡∏à‡∏∞‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡∏î‡∏≠‡∏Å‡πÄ‡∏ö‡∏µ‡πâ‡∏¢ <strong>{accountInfo.interestRate * 10} ‡∏ø</strong> ‡∏ï‡πà‡∏≠‡∏™‡∏±‡∏õ‡∏î‡∏≤‡∏´‡πå
